Package: dlmLesion
Type: Package
Title: Dynamic Prediction of Lesion Voxel Trajectories in Individuals with Multiple Sclerosis
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Jordan Johns
Maintainer: Jordan Johns <jordan.tjohns@gmail.com>
Description: Takes voxel trajectories from MS lesions and preprocesses the trajectories for dynamic prediction and visualization. Standardizes voxel trajectories with respect to baseline intensity levels.  Interpolates intensities at a specified grid of points.  Dynamically predicts future trajectories using historical information and demographic variables for voxels currently in the dataset and new emerging lesions.  Provides visualization functions to examine predictions of trajectories and lesion slices
License: None
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
Depends:
    plyr,
    tidyverse,
    reshape2,
    gridExtra,
    ggplot2,
    Hmisc
Suggests: knitr, 
    rmarkdown,
    lubridate
VignetteBuilder: knitr
RoxygenNote: 6.1.1
